Description: Vera Bradley Metropolitan Bag – Nantucket Navy - Retired The pattern, Nantucket Navy was introduced in 2005 and retired in 2007. Authentic Vera Bradley. There is also a zippered pocket on one side of the interior and two open slip pockets (great place for phone) on the other side.Replace that old bag that you love with a new one.
